{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitem"]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}],"title":"OUDSCheckboxItem","symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents16OUDSCheckboxItemV"},"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"reference"},{"text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components with labels and icons.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a checkbox with only an indicator prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/init(isOn:label:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:action:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/body"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"content":[{"anchor":"Layouts","text":"Layouts","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reversed"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing checkbox indicator and a leading optional image"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Indicator-states","text":"Indicator states","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you are looking for a checkbox component with three states, use instead "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom checkbox trait."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDSThemesContract side as this value remains in the users hands."}]},{"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}]},{"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","type":"heading","level":2},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\")","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Bazinga!\", helper: \"Doll-Dagga Buzz-Buzz Ziggety-Zag\")","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn,","                     label: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                     helper: \"Of dreaming boys and wide-eyed girls\",","                     isReversed: true,","                     icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn,","                     label: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                     isError: true,","                     errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                     hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to manage the RTL mode quite easily and switch your layouts (flip image, indicator in RTL leading i.e. in the right):"}]},{"code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $selection,","                     labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                     icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                     flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                     isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Suggestions","text":"Suggestions","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox\/b\/6578e5\/t\/3dd013a529"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}]},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading","level":2},{"anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","text":"Orange Business Tools","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkboxItem_OrangeBusinessTools"}]},{"anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Wireframe"}]},{"style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"2.3.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"Version"},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Since"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSCheckboxItem/init(isOn:label:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:action:)":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/init(isOn:label:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:action:)","abstract":[{"text":"Creates a checkbox with label and optional helper text, icon, divider.","type":"text"}],"title":"init(isOn:label:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:action:)","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitem\/init(ison:label:helper:icon:flipicon:isreversed:iserror:errortext:isreadonly:hasdivider:action:)","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"isOn","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Binding","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI7BindingV"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":">, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"label","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"helper","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"icon","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Image","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI5ImageV"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"flipIcon","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kin